Based on the provided data for the Instagram account @toofaced, here's what I can tell you:

The account has 12,484,905 followers and follows 2,274 accounts. They have made 12,334 posts. The account is verified and classified as a Business Account in the "Personal Goods & General Merchandise Stores" category.
